{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"cp-hero-001","type":"text","text":"# Consistent Parallax â€” Content Architecture\n\nA guided parallax tour of wod.wiki, structured as five narrative acts plus supplementary sections.\n\n**Sample Workout:**\n```wod\n5 Pushups\n:10 Rest\n5 Pushups\n```\n\n**Flow:** Write â†’ Track â†’ Rest â†’ Review â†’ Records\n\n**Key Principle:** Each act is a `ParallaxSection` with step descriptors. Runtime-dependent acts share a single `ScopedRuntimeProvider`. Interactive triggers (Run, Next, Complete) drive cross-section scroll transitions.","x":-300,"y":-1400,"width":600,"height":340,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"cp-act1-002","type":"text","text":"# Act 1 â€” Journal Your Workout\n\n**Sticky Panel:** Editor (frozen, readonly)\n**Runtime:** None\n\n**Steps:**\n1. Load note, empty state â†’ \"It's a journal with funky highlighting\"\n2. Color coding explained â€” green (movement), blue (timer), orange (reps), purple (effort)\n3. Run button â€” inline + wod block header â†’ triggers runtime.start() + scroll to Act 2\n\n**Key Element:** The Run â–¶ button appears both inline in the narrative text and in the wod block header. Clicking either starts the runtime.\n\n**Exit Transition:** `runtime.start()` â†’ `scrollIntoView('#act-2')`","x":-1100,"y":-900,"width":480,"height":380,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"cp-act2-003","type":"text","text":"# Act 2 â€” Track: Pushups\n\n**Sticky Panel:** Track Panel (live runtime)\n**Runtime:** ScopedRuntimeProvider (shared with Acts 3-4)\n\n**Steps:**\n1. Timer counting up â€” no time set on block, so count-up mode\n2. Context â€” child of rounds block, inherits parent scope\n3. Next button â€” inline clone of Track Panel button â†’ `runtime.next()` + scroll to Act 3\n\n**Key Element:** The \"next card\" preview shows `:10 Rest` as the upcoming block.\n\n**Exit Transition:** `runtime.next()` â†’ `scrollIntoView('#act-3')`","x":-300,"y":-900,"width":480,"height":380,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"cp-act3-004","type":"text","text":"# Act 3 â€” Track: Rest\n\n**Sticky Panel:** Track Panel (same runtime)\n**Runtime:** Same ScopedRuntimeProvider as Act 2\n\n**Steps:**\n1. Rest countdown â€” `:10` timer counts down from 10 seconds\n2. Last block â€” next card is empty, click Next to finish\n\n**Key Element:** Next card indicator changes to empty, signaling last block.\n\n**Auto-Advance:** Timer completion fires `runtime.complete` â†’ scroll to Act 4\n**Manual Override:** Next button â†’ `runtime.next()` â†’ scroll to Act 4","x":500,"y":-900,"width":480,"height":360,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"cp-act4-005","type":"text","text":"# Act 4 â€” Review Metrics\n\n**Sticky Panel:** Review Panel (ReviewGrid)\n**Runtime:** Same ScopedRuntimeProvider (reads completed runtime)\n\n**Steps:**\n1. Micro-metrics â€” duration, reps, effort per segment\n2. Projection engines â€” Volume, Rep, Distance, SessionLoad, MetMinute\n3. Calculated projections â€” total volume, total reps, session load\n\n**Data Pipeline:**\n```\nScriptRuntime.outputStatements\n  â†’ AnalyticsTransformer\n    â†’ Segment[] (with metrics)\n      â†’ Projection engines\n        â†’ ProjectionResult[]\n          â†’ ReviewGrid\n```","x":-1100,"y":-380,"width":480,"height":400,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"cp-act5-006","type":"text","text":"# Act 5 â€” Back to Editor\n\n**Sticky Panel:** Editor (with runtime records)\n**Runtime:** None (runtime disposed after Act 4)\n\n**Steps:**\n1. Records visible â€” runtime output entries below the wod block\n2. Coming soon â€” reports and historical tracking\n\n**Key Element:** The editor now shows the completed runtime's output/log entries embedded below the wod code block.\n\n**Exit Transition:** Continue scrolling to supplementary sections","x":-300,"y":-380,"width":480,"height":320,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"cp-runtime-007","type":"text","text":"# Runtime Scoping\n\n**Scope Boundary:** Acts 2, 3, 4\n\n```\n<ParallaxSection> {/* Act 1: Editor */}\n  <FrozenEditorPanel />\n</ParallaxSection>\n\n<ScopedRuntimeProvider>\n  <ParallaxSection> {/* Act 2: Pushups */}\n    <LiveTrackerPanel />\n  </ParallaxSection>\n  <ParallaxSection> {/* Act 3: Rest */}\n    <LiveTrackerPanel />\n  </ParallaxSection>\n  <ParallaxSection> {/* Act 4: Review */}\n    <ReviewPanel />\n  </ParallaxSection>\n</ScopedRuntimeProvider>\n\n<ParallaxSection> {/* Act 5: Editor + Records */}\n  <FrozenEditorPanel showRecords />\n</ParallaxSection>\n```\n\n**Lifecycle:**\n- Created when Act 2 scrolls into view\n- Persists through Acts 3 and 4\n- Disposed when user scrolls past Act 4","x":500,"y":-380,"width":480,"height":540,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"cp-collections-008","type":"text","text":"# Collections Section\n\n**Layout:** ScrollSection with Editor Panel + Collection Browser\n**Runtime:** Config 3 (fullscreen dialog for Run)\n\n**Features:**\n- List all built-in collections from `wod-collections.ts`\n- Click collection â†’ CommandPalette with `collectionStrategy`\n- Select workout â†’ loads into editor (in-memory)\n- Run button â†’ fullscreen Track â†’ Review flow\n\n**Note to user:** \"In-memory only â€” data does not persist on reload.\"\n\n**Journal Subsection:**\n- Calendar view / weekly planner\n- Markdown editor with embedded context\n- Sideloaded data (GPX files)\n- Informational only â€” no interactive demo","x":-1100,"y":300,"width":480,"height":420,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"cp-chromecast-009","type":"text","text":"# Chromecast Feature Callout\n\n**Layout:** ScrollSection with illustration\n\n**Message:**\n\"Cast your workouts to your TV. Use the remote as your lap timer â€” the perfect companion for the home gym.\"\n\n**Technical:** WebRTC transport via `CastTransport` â†’ Chromecast receiver (`receiver-rpc.tsx`)\n\n**Personal Note:** Core driving feature of the developer who built wod.wiki â€” designed for the home gym workout experience.\n\n**Cast Policy:** Only available from Journal pages (Config 3). Not shown during parallax demo or Collections browse.","x":-300,"y":300,"width":480,"height":340,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"cp-deepdive-010","type":"text","text":"# Deep Dive Section\n\n**Layout:** ScrollSection with resource links\n\n**Resources:**\n- **Syntax Reference** (`/syntax`) â€” Complete WhiteboardScript language reference\n- **Getting Started** (`/getting-started`) â€” 6-level progressive tutorial (Zero to Hero)\n- **Playground** (`/playground`) â€” Interactive editor with full runtime\n\n**Purpose:** After the guided tour, point users to self-service learning resources for deeper exploration.","x":500,"y":300,"width":480,"height":280,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"cp-triggers-011","type":"text","text":"# Interactive Trigger Map\n\n| Trigger | Act | Action | Scroll Target |\n|---------|-----|--------|---------------|\n| â–¶ Run | 1â†’2 | `runtime.start()` | `#act-2` |\n| â–¶â–¶ Next | 2â†’3 | `runtime.next()` | `#act-3` |\n| âŹ± Timer done | 3â†’4 | auto-complete | `#act-4` |\n| â–¶â–¶ Next (manual) | 3â†’4 | `runtime.next()` | `#act-4` |\n| Runtime complete | 4 | `onComplete` | `#act-4` |\n\n**Scroll Behavior:**\n- `scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' })`\n- `prefers-reduced-motion` â†’ `behavior: 'auto'`\n- 500ms debounce on rapid triggers\n- `ScrollSource: 'user' | 'runtime'` anti-loop","x":-1100,"y":860,"width":480,"height":380,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"cp-responsive-012","type":"text","text":"# Responsive Layout\n\n**Desktop (â‰Ą1024px):**\n- Sticky panel: 60% width (left)\n- Step text: 40% width (right)\n- IntersectionObserver rootMargin: `-30% 0px -30% 0px`\n\n**Tablet (768â€“1023px):**\n- Same layout with reduced margins\n- Panels adjust to 50/50 split\n\n**Mobile (<768px):**\n- Sticky panel: top (40vh, 320px min)\n- Steps: stacked below\n- rootMargin: `-65px 0px -20% 0px`\n- `prefers-reduced-motion`: no transform transitions\n\n**StickyNav sections:**\n`Write | Track | Rest | Review | Records | Collections | Cast | Dive`","x":-300,"y":860,"width":480,"height":380,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"cp-nav-013","type":"text","text":"# Navigation & Deep Linking\n\n**Anchor IDs:**\n- `#act-1` â€” Journal Your Workout\n- `#act-2` â€” Track: Pushups\n- `#act-3` â€” Track: Rest\n- `#act-4` â€” Review Metrics\n- `#act-5` â€” Back to Editor\n- `#collections` â€” Collections\n- `#chromecast` â€” Chromecast\n- `#deep-dive` â€” Deep Dive\n\n**StickyNavPanel:** `hero-follow` variant\n- Appears after hero scroll-out\n- Highlights active section via IntersectionObserver\n- Click navigates via `scrollIntoView()`\n\n**External Links:**\n- Other pages can link to `/#act-2` to jump directly to the tracker demo","x":500,"y":860,"width":480,"height":400,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"cp-pipeline-014","type":"text","text":"# Panel Transition Choreography\n\n```\nAct 1 (Editor frozen)\n  â”‚ Run â–¶\n  â–Ľ\nAct 2 (Track â€” count up)\n  â”‚ Next â–¶â–¶\n  â–Ľ\nAct 3 (Track â€” countdown)\n  â”‚ Timer done / Next â–¶â–¶\n  â–Ľ\nAct 4 (Review grid)\n  â”‚ scroll\n  â–Ľ\nAct 5 (Editor + records)\n  â”‚ scroll\n  â–Ľ\nCollections (ScrollSection)\n  â”‚ scroll\n  â–Ľ\nChromecast (ScrollSection)\n  â”‚ scroll\n  â–Ľ\nDeep Dive (ScrollSection)\n```\n\n**Sticky panel content is determined by active ParallaxSection.**\nEach section renders its own sticky content â€” no global panel switch logic needed.","x":1100,"y":-900,"width":400,"height":520,"color":"4"}
	],
